              title: "Apply Law 2 — Engineer Attractiveness",
              description: "Identify one thing you genuinely enjoy and bundle it with the new habit using Milkman's temptation bundling formula: you only access the enjoyable thing during or immediately after the new habit. Additionally, practice the reframe: change your self-talk from 'I have to do this' to 'I get to do this' or 'I choose to do this.' Small as it sounds, this autonomy framing has measurable effects on motivation persistence over time."
            },
